When INSRTP is non-nil or called-interactively insert sha1 on newline.\n
Does not move point.\n
:SEE-ALSO `sha1-region', `sha1-string'.\n▶▶▶."
  (interactive "r\ni\np")
  (eval-when-compile (require 'sha1))
  (let ((sha1-r (sha1-region start end)))
